dct_description_sm: Map was published for La Holland-America Line. Map includes sites of interest depicted pictorially. Holland-America Line offices are located on map. On verso: bird's eye view of area of quartier de la Madeleine et de l'Opéra (extrait du Plan de Paris à vol d'oiseau / Blondel la Rougery 1956) and map of Paris-Métro. © Blondel la Rougery 1958. "Tous droits des reproduction, même partielle, strictement réservés."
